## 🛠️ Useful Docker Commands

- **View running containers**:
  ```bash
  docker ps
  ```
- **View container logs**:
  ```bash
  docker logs -f <container_name_or_id>
  ```
- **Stop a running container**:
  ```bash
  docker stop <container_name_or_id>
  ```
- **Clean up unused Docker resources**:
  ```bash
  docker system prune -a --volumes
  ```

